	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p>Skilled craftspeople in the realm of fashion are usually multitalented. As tailors, they use organic and inorganic fibers and cloths to create clothing. As beauticians, they use cosmetics to dye hair and apply makeup.</p><p></p><ul><li><p><strong>Skill Advantage:</strong> A person skilled at fashion has &amp;reference[advantage] on checks involving clothes and makeup, including but not limited to some &amp;reference[Deception], &amp;reference[History], &amp;reference[Intimidation], &amp;reference[Perception], and &amp;reference[Religion] checks.</p></li><li><p><strong>Craft:</strong> A fashion designer can craft one of the following over a long rest:</p><ul><li><p><strong>Armor:</strong> @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-equipment.Item.jSi9ralAm7FzUQbH]{Padded Armor}.*</p></li><li><p><strong>Clothes:</strong> @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-equipment.Item.IjPxHzAFBAujZwvU]{Common Clothes}, @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-equipment.Item.CBoKcO4S8XZQ94hU]{Cold Weather Clothes}, @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-equipment.Item.Ys0moTTTz4gHsRsE]{Fine Clothes}, @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-equipment.Item.f3hzLiXSl5eoWB6i]{Noble Clothes}, @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-equipment.Item.X9pqM4zh4jo5WsPV]{Robe}, @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-equipment.Item.FKOeQFXKm1ZxhBcl]{Traveler's Clothes}, @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-equipment.Item.hIMF5UDtyBiAHWPT]{Uniform}.</p></li><li><p><strong>Misc:</strong> @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-equipment.Item.Wn0qne5xLaRD7Qhx]{Blanket}, @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-equipment.Item.ZLVQ3RdLsElx1gfw]{String} (10 ft.).</p></li></ul></li></ul><p><span style=\"font-weight:bold\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><em><strong>*</strong></em></span><span style=\"font-style:italic\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><em>Â Magic padded armor uses the statistics of magic leather armor.</em></span></p>",
